Prettier Ignore File

Defines files and directories that Prettier should ignore when formatting.

-----------------

BUILD OUTPUT

-----------------

Ignore compiled output folders

/build
/dist
/out
/tmp
/public
/coverage

-----------------

DEPENDENCIES

-----------------

Ignore all third-party dependencies (node modules)

/node_modules

-----------------

LOGS AND TEMP

-----------------

Ignore logs and miscellaneous temp files

*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

-----------------

CONFIG & CACHE

-----------------

Common configuration and cache files

.cache
.env
.env.local
.git
.idea
.vscode

-----------------

FRAMEWORK SPECIFIC (Add/Remove as needed)

-----------------

Gatsby

.cache/
public/

Next.js

.next/

SvelteKit

.svelte-kit/